data.meta_description: He was a son of Mr. and Mrs. Frank Marlenee. He married Margaret Darchuk at Wolf Point on November 23, 1932. She died in 1969.  Survivors include three sons, Ronald and Lanny, both of Scobey and Robert of Plentywood; two sisters, Mrs. Elsie Shaw of Kennewick, WA and Mrs. Ethel Strillmatter, Fallbrook CA; two brothers,...
